++ [[span style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #a12d25, #730000); color: #ffffff; padding: 5px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 40px; line-height: 1.9;"]]{{**Project BLACKBOX Vote Summary**}}[[/span]]
