"//This is not who we are. This is not who they were. Were any of you at the wedding? I know y'all weren't-- I was Mal's maid of honor. Their love was a powerful thing, hell, she remembered Maddy's name long after she lost her own, even if it was in the wrong place. And this,// this //is what you wish to do with their legacy?//"

